{"lemma":"رَطْلَيْ","slug":"رَطْلَيْ","root":"ر.ط.ل","root_slug":"ر-ط-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ط-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15804","n15808","n15809"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rottol, a historical Middle Eastern and North African unit of dry weight equal to 1–5 pounds (0.5–2.5 kg)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pound"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Aramaic רִיטְלָא / ܪܺܝܛܠܳܐ (rīṭlā), earlier לִיטְרָא / ܠܺܝܛܪܳܐ (līṭrā), from Ancient Greek λίτρα (lítra). Doublet of لِتْر (litr), a later French loanword."},"ipa":["/ritˤl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15804","headword_ar":"رَطَلَ","root":"rTl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raTolN","text_ar":"رَطْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He weighed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing: (O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put in motion"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weighed with his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tried"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that he might know its weight"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also 2.] But IF says, of this combination of letters and the like, that they are not of the genuine language [of the Arabs]. (O.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ran;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaA","text_ar":"عَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["O","Msb","K","TA","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n15808","headword_ar":"رَطْلٌ","root":"rTl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riTolN","text_ar":"رِطْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, lax,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompact;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muroTilN","text_ar":"مُرْطِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old and weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining to softness, and laxness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompactness, and old age:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and a boy"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender, slim,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or, as some say, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near to attaining puberty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virility:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose bones have not become strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the former, applied to a boy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose strength has not become fully established;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muroTalN","text_ar":"مُرْطَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus written with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"T","text_ar":"ط"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riTalapN","text_ar":"رِطَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, TA:) and the first, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raTolN","text_ar":"رَطْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a man who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foolish; stupid; unsound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficient, in intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possesses not, what suffices;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is not profitable to any one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having flaccid ears:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) and, applied to a horse, (Ibn- 'Abbád, O, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riTolN","text_ar":"رِطْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or, as some say, the latter only, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, TA,) in all the senses. (TA.)       -A2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aTolu","text_ar":"الرَّطْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also explained in the K as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEadolu","text_ar":"العَدْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but perhaps this is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEadowu","text_ar":"العَدْوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaA","text_ar":"عَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, last sentence.]       -A3-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n15809","headword_ar":"رِطْلٌ","root":"rTl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raTolN","text_ar":"رَطْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) the former of which is the better known, (Msb, TA,) or the more chaste, (O, TA,) [but the latter is that which is now in common use,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain thing with which one weighs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which one uses as a measure of capacity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) [or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"both: a pound-weight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pint-measure:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pound"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pint"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything:] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manFA","text_ar":"مَنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) accord. to the standard of Baghdád,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve ounces; the ounce"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uwqiy~ap","text_ar":"اُوقِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isotaAr","text_ar":"اـِسْتَار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and two thirds of an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstAr","text_ar":"استار"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstAr","text_ar":"استار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being four"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAqiyl","text_ar":"مَثَاقِيل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and half of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivoqaAl","text_ar":"مِثْقَال"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mvqAl","text_ar":"مثقال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diroham","text_ar":"دِرْهَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and three sevenths of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drhm","text_ar":"درهم"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drhm","text_ar":"درهم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being six"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dawaAniq","text_ar":"دَوَانِق"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAniq","text_ar":"دَانِق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being eight"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hab~aAt","text_ar":"حَبَّات"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and two fifths of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hab~ap","text_ar":"حَبَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is ninety"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mvAqyl","text_ar":"مثاقيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hundred and twenty-eight"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraAhim","text_ar":"دَرَاهِم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and four sevenths of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drhm","text_ar":"درهم"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or, accord. to A 'Obeyd,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hundred and twenty-eight"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the weight of seven"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazona saboEapK","text_ar":"وَزْنَ سَبْعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[explained voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirohamN","text_ar":"دِرْهَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]): (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve ounces; the ounce"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uwqiy~ap","text_ar":"اُوقِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. the ounce of the Arabs, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being forty"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the whole is four hundred and eighty"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, TA:) this is the Syrian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and thus it is, accord. to El-Harbee, in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~un~apu fiY","text_ar":"السُّنَّةُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ikaAHi riTolN","text_ar":"النِّكَاحِ رِطْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The usage"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Prophet"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of marriage was"},{"kind":"text","text":"to give"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of silver]: (Mgh, TA:) so says Az in the T: (Mgh:) or, as is [also] said by Az, it is in this instance"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve ounces and a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"na$~","text_ar":"نَشّ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n$~","text_ar":"نشّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being twenty"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the whole is five hundred"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drAhm","text_ar":"دراهم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as is related on the authority of 'Áïsheh: but in a trad. 'Omar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve ounces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"without the mention of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n$~","text_ar":"نشّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to the lawyers, [however,] when the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is mentioned without restriction, what is meant thereby is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Baghdád: (TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a measure of capacity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] it is said in the A [&c.] to be the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eighth part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAE","text_ar":"صَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mud~","text_ar":"مُدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"man~","text_ar":"مَنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the vessels of the vintner"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. because it contains a pint]: (Har p. 650:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroTaAlN","text_ar":"اَرْطَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raTolN","text_ar":"رَطْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}